{"tid":1800892,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"曱甴：朗豪坊嘅玻璃係暴徒打爛 而唔係催淚彈","createTime":"2019-12-28T08:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T09:06:59.000Z","uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c29ff330a642441e0f43cb8d2c950ba7964c1c50","tid":1800892,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"【催淚彈射破商舖玻璃？】(2019-12-27)<br />\n<br />\n有謠言指在平安夜晚上，警方發射催淚彈射破旺角一間商舖的玻璃。事實是當晚約十時，五名暴徒以硬物打破該店舖的玻璃後逃走。<br />\n<br />\nOnline rumours allege that on Christmas Eve, tear gas canisters fired by Police officers broke the glass pane of a shop in Mongkok. The truth is at around 10 pm, rioters broke the glass with hard objects and fled.<br />\n<br />\n#假新聞假消息<br />\n#警方澄清<br />\n#切勿跟車太貼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJb0Mzc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJb0Mzc.png&h=f9302386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c97556da12279bb1cfee4c1d0f05d04f14c7c2","tid":1800892,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"=.="},{"pid":"0914d0a7b87e8853eea43c7074fa330464536df7","tid":1800892,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n[告急] 德國人權法30號截,差22K, 用chrome簽, chrome可以幫你翻譯做中文, 唔撚洗睇教學都識簽</span><br />\n<br />\n洗撚睇教學咩<br />\n<br />\n直接right click 轉做中文啦 好撚易之嘛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=290f8aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJuUQZm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJuUQZm.png&h=